WEBVTT

00:03.663 --> 00:07.943
Transcript provided by: Team
CreepySubs Twitter.Com/creepysubs.

00:07.944 --> 00:10.893
We said, "is there a friendly spirit here?"

00:10.894 --> 00:13.414
It said "no".

00:13.515 --> 00:14.416
Hey!

00:14.417 --> 00:16.514
Something odd was happening in the house.

00:16.515 --> 00:19.142
What have we done? What have we done?

00:19.143 --> 00:22.031
It's like a long streak and it
had fire coming out of its back.

00:22.032 --> 00:24.400
This woman thinks she is seeing a UFO.

00:24.401 --> 00:26.919
- I could hear her nervousness.
- But it's not moving.

00:26.920 --> 00:30.116
All of a sudden everything
electronic in my vehicle dies.

00:30.117 --> 00:31.502
998, do you read me?

00:31.503 --> 00:33.550
Any unit who doesn't
answer, that's a crisis.

00:33.551 --> 00:35.666
Do you read me?

00:35.667 --> 00:40.158
I really knew that I was not
alone in that house anymore.

00:40.159 --> 00:43.318
I was scared it was going
to hurt one of us.

00:43.319 --> 00:45.963
My hand was right on my pistol.

00:45.964 --> 00:48.979
It was weird, wait a minute oh
my God, I ain't ready for this.

00:48.980 --> 00:51.920
It was unbelievable.

